title: Unloading Jet fuel, diesel underway at harbour: Minister
body_lines: Energy and Power Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said that jet fuel and diesel which have been freighted into the country are currently being unloaded at the harbour.
Meanwhile, he asked the public to help island-wide fuel distribution without any hindrances and guarantee the safety of fuel bowsers and fuel wagons hauled by trains. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)
